  "text": "Planning for 3D-CRT, s-IMRT, and mARC was performed for the ten patients with thoracic esophageal cancer. The mean PTV volume was 413.88 ± 184.58 cm [CITATION_1] , and the mean total volume of the lung and heart were 3,602.06 ± 869.26 cm [CITATION_2] and 678.39 ± 135.94 cm 3 , respectively. Table 1 summarizes the clinical stage, location of metastatic nodes, total volume and long axis for PTV, and the total volume of the lung and heart in each patient.",
